{"tid":1178802,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇左netflix港產片 家和萬左驚？幾正  (吳鎮宇, 袁詠儀, 古天樂)","createTime":"2019-05-30T16:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T08:54:10.000Z","uid":72269,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9ae5ba4110c01f5e264c81dfbb62a75e056ba65","tid":1178802,"uid":72269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:02:55.000Z","msg":"原本睇trailer色水以為係大陸野<br />\n睇睇下見邱禮濤個名決定睇落去<br />\n之前完全唔知有套咁嘅野上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但出乎以料幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n套野舞台劇改篇<br />\n真係成套都好舞台劇feel<br />\n上網睇返少得可憐嘅影評<br />\n多數都屌套野誇9張演員演技大暴走<br />\n但我又覺得只要唔抱住睇劇情片嘅心態<br />\n就覺得呢種誇張痴線嘅演繹<br />\n真係好反映到今時今日呢個痴線社會<br />\n只有香港人睇先會睇到咁入肉同唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後劇情大暴走，一開頭都接受唔到<br />\n但當諗下現實幾多野一樣咁荒謬<br />\n就覺得呢個結局好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一覺得真係9唔搭8就係黃秋生條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋原來原著劇本<br />\n亞 Dum 一家看海的日子<br />\n已經係93年嘅作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415e4308468ac701562793c6c830853f1361f46d","tid":1178802,"uid":71527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n睇過，係幾正"},{"pid":"9992bf55da3107205129293a436f687c7e4c82ba","tid":1178802,"uid":154684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"年頭上戲院咁快上netflix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba4efbd0d101f9be5ae3426fe9537d60619c995","tid":1178802,"uid":72269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9992bf55da3107205129293a436f687c7e4c82ba","tid":1178802,"uid":154684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"年頭上戲院咁快上netflix<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"應該係票房太差拿拿臨賣比netflix<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7d3380576d17d58f5a0d824ee7be5ae6913972","tid":1178802,"uid":11738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"套戲好嘈<br />\n個尾幾特別"},{"pid":"8a4be485c052d67e13db5781cae394b8cd213c68","tid":1178802,"uid":15213,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"賀歲前果排入戲院睇咗<br />\n我覺得成套風格就係痴痴地線同壓抑得嚟又充滿黑色幽默<br />\n達明同鎮宇天橋果幕都睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢班主角加埋客串果班卡士都值千萬票房<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜上果時冇乜宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf6e03816f6d8a392a6cb166da8ebcbabfb17b14","tid":1178802,"uid":206762,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:45:16.000Z","msg":"呢類黑色幽默係香港真係少之又少 上個陣票房又唔係幾好 但我極中意呢套作品 既寫實又荒誕 最尾屋企個part 當你以為所有野都完既時候 導演補多下 令你知道呢家人已經去到無可救藥既地步 將佢地既痴線再推上高峰<br />\n記得上個陣有推 但都幫唔到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4264e5cd165202de3445b46bdaaa92e93437720","tid":1178802,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"靴蚊邱出品 必屬佳品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cbd5477fdefbd77a3b66a22e8aafebd8b0439e","tid":1178802,"uid":86277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"好痴線，最痴線係個故事好真實，發生喺香港一啲都唔出奇"},{"pid":"f2011201cfc0597ff1163bb25796967d27e77230","tid":1178802,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"偽港產 大陸陣味整唔甩 不了"},{"pid":"7fc7160e62eb9237434aedc78107bad95f647c99","tid":11